 "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Invoice</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n        max-width: 800px;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n        text-align: left;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .logo-container {\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n    }\n\n    .logo {\n        max-width: 200px;\n    }\n\n    .address {\n        font-size: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .letter {\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    \n        .line {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n\n    .labels {\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 120px;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n\n    .colon {\n        /*margin-right: 10px;*/\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <p>Authorised Sales & Service Parts Dealer</p>\n            <div class=\"logo-container\">\n                <div>\n                    <img class=\"logo\" src=\"https://dcautoservices.mydotconsulting.com/files/perodua-logo.png\" alt=\"Company Logo 1\" width=\"200\">\n                    <div class=\"address\">\n                        <b>ROHAMAS PRO AUTOSERV SDN BHD <span style=\"font-size:10px\">(786823-T)</span></b><br>\n                        Lot 91517 Persiaran Atmosfera Seksyen U5<br>\n                        40150 Shah Alam Selangor<br>\n                        Tel: 012-8835282 <br>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!--\n                <img class=\"logo\" src=\"\" alt=\"Company Logo 2\" width=\"200\" height=\"45\">\n                -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"letter\">\n                \n                 <p style=\"text-align: center; text-decoration:underline\">   <strong>Letter of Undertaking</strong><br></p>\n                   <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">Date</span><span class=\"colon\">:</span>\n                    <span>{{ frappe.utils.formatdate(doc.date_issued, \"dd MMMM yyyy\") }}</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">To</span><span class=\"colon\">:</span>\n                    <span>HONG LEONG ISLAMIC BANK BERHAD</span>\n                </div>\n                    \n                    <p style=\"text-align: left;\">Dear Sir/Madam,<br><br></p>\n                    \n                    <p style=\"text-align: left; text-decoration:underline\"> <strong>Re: Crediting of Hire Purchase (HP) Disbursement through UOB Account via Online</strong></p> <br>\n                    \n                     <p style=\"text-align: left;\">We refer to HP financing provided by your bank to our car buyer.<br><br>\n                    \n                    We would like irrevocably instruct your bank that all the HP disbursement of the loan amount and handling fees to be credited into our <b>UOB via online account no: 9123006239 - in the name of ROHAMAS PRO AUTOSERV SDN BHD</b><br><br>\n                    \n                    We shall be grateful if you will let us have payment as soon as possible. Your co-operation is highly appreciated.<br><br>\n                    \n                    Thank you.<br><br>\n                    Yours faithfully,<br>\n                      <img src=\"https://rohamas.mydotconsulting.com/files/sign%20fairuz.jpg\" width=\"70\" height=\"50\">\n                    <img src=\"https://rohamas.mydotconsulting.com/files/cop%20rohamas%20(1).png\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\"><br>\n                    \n                    -------------------------------------------- <br>\n                    MOHD FAIRUZ BIN MOHD HAMDAN\n                    \n                    \n                    \n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
